{
  "name": "Se7enSlasher - Harmonic Squares (The Dance of the Squares)",
  "description": "",
  "frame_eqs": "spd=0.95; sm=0.5;\njustin_bieber=1; is_gay=1;\nbieber_is_gay=equal(justin_bieber,is_gay);\n\nq1=(bass+mid+treb)/3;\nq2=(bass_att+mid_att+treb_att)/3;\n\ndc=pow(0.99,30/fps);\ncv=max(max(bass,mid),treb);\ncvs=cvs*dc+cv*(1-dc);\nb=above(cv,cvs+pk)*above(time,tb+0.2);\ntb=time*b+tb*(1-b);\npk=pk*0.9*(1-b)+b*cvs;\n\nq3=xt; q4=yt;\nq5=dt;\nq6=xp; q7=yp;\n\n// Fractal movement (xt-, yt-)\nxt=xt*spd+xts*(1-spd); yt=yt*spd+yts*(1-spd);\n\n// Portal movement (dt-)\ndt=dt*spd+dts*(1-spd);\n\n// Portal XY position\nxp=xp*spd+xps*(1-spd); yp=yp*spd+yps*(1-spd);\n\nxts=xts*sm+xtsc*(1-sm); yts=yts*sm+ytsc*(1-sm);\ndts=dts*sm+dtsc*(1-sm);\nxps=xps*sm+xpsc*(1-sm); yps=yps*sm+ypsc*(1-sm);\n\nxtsc=if(b,(rand(200)-100)/200,xtsc);\nytsc=if(b,(rand(200)-100)/200,ytsc);\ndtsc=if(b,rand(100)/100*bieber_is_gay,dtsc);\nxpsc=if(b,(rand(200)-100)/250,xpsc);\nypsc=if(b,(rand(200)-100)/250,ypsc);\n\nq9=dtsc;",
